   20: -module(sets_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   23: 
   24: -compile(export_all).
   25: -compile(nowarn_export_all).
   26: 
   27: all() ->
   28:     [
   29:         add_element_case,
   30:         del_element_case,
   31:         filter_case,
   32:         filtermap_case,
   33:         fold_case,
   34: 	from_list_case,
   35:         intersection_1_case,
   36:         intersection_2_case,
   37:         is_disjoint_case,
   38:         is_element_case,
   39:         is_empty_case,
   40:         is_equal_case,
   41:         is_set_case,
   42:         is_subset_case,
   43: 	map_case,
   44:         size_case,
   45:         subtract_case,
   46:         to_list_case,
   47:         union_1_case,
   48:         union_2_case,
   49: 	operations_case
   50:     ].
   51: 
   52: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   53:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   54: 
   55: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   56:     Config.
   57: 
   58: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
   59:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(sets_prop:Prop(), Config).
   60: 
   61: add_element_case(Config) ->
   62:     do_proptest(prop_add_element, Config).
   63: 
   64: del_element_case(Config) ->
   65:     do_proptest(prop_del_element, Config).
   66: 
   67: filter_case(Config) ->
   68:     do_proptest(prop_filter, Config).
   69: 
   70: filtermap_case(Config) ->
   71:     do_proptest(prop_filtermap, Config).
   72: 
   73: fold_case(Config) ->
   74:     do_proptest(prop_fold, Config).
   75: 
   76: from_list_case(Config) ->
   77:     do_proptest(prop_from_list, Config).
   78: 
   79: intersection_1_case(Config) ->
   80:     do_proptest(prop_intersection_1, Config).
   81: 
   82: intersection_2_case(Config) ->
   83:     do_proptest(prop_intersection_2, Config).
   84: 
   85: is_disjoint_case(Config) ->
   86:     do_proptest(prop_is_disjoint, Config).
   87: 
   88: is_element_case(Config) ->
   89:     do_proptest(prop_is_element, Config).
   90: 
   91: is_empty_case(Config) ->
   92:     do_proptest(prop_is_empty, Config).
   93: 
   94: is_equal_case(Config) ->
   95:     do_proptest(prop_is_equal, Config).
   96: 
   97: is_set_case(Config) ->
   98:     do_proptest(prop_is_set, Config).
   99: 
  100: is_subset_case(Config) ->
  101:     do_proptest(prop_is_subset, Config).
  102: 
  103: map_case(Config) ->
  104:     do_proptest(prop_map, Config).
  105: 
  106: size_case(Config) ->
  107:     do_proptest(prop_size, Config).
  108: 
  109: subtract_case(Config) ->
  110:     do_proptest(prop_subtract, Config).
  111: 
  112: to_list_case(Config) ->
  113:     do_proptest(prop_to_list, Config).
  114: 
  115: union_1_case(Config) ->
  116:     do_proptest(prop_union_1, Config).
  117: 
  118: union_2_case(Config) ->
  119:     do_proptest(prop_union_2, Config).
  120: 
  121: operations_case(Config) ->
